<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF646ADBFA5D974016F6BA6C" pageId="159" pageNumber="920" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF646ADBFA5D974016F6BA6C" blockId="159.[1440,2646,281,471]" pageId="159" pageNumber="920">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF646ADBFA5D97401900BA04" bold="true" box="[1441,1792,281,310]" pageId="159" pageNumber="920">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Hidden Tube-nosed Bat does not seem to face any major threats.
</paragraph>
